OL,3,C'Woeful budgeting' in Home Office
OL,4,Ccausing overspends on asylum
OL,6,F"Woeful budgeting" at the Home Office
OL,7,Fhas caused repeated overspends on the
OL,8,Fasylum system, a fiscal watchdog has
OL,9,Fwarned.
OL,11,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies (IFS)
OL,12,Fsaid the department has frequently
OL,13,Fspent far more than it had budgeted
OL,14,Ffor asylum, border, visa and passport
OL,15,Foperations.
OL,17,FIt says the budget for 2024/25 is
OL,18,Frepeating mistakes made under the
OL,19,Fprevious government by submitting
OL,20,Ffigures it "knows to be insufficient".
